headline.main: Team Israel Keen to Show They Belong at WBC
headline.print_headline: Team Israel Keen to Show They Belong at WBC

lead_paragraph: To players on Team Israel, it doesn't matter that they don't live in Israel and play ball in the United States, don't speak Hebrew and haven't visited the country until recently.
